title: Most disappointing teams & toaster games
itunes:title: Most disappointing teams & toaster games
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – review the latest headlines around the league including Martavis Bryant's suspension and Junior Galette's season-ending injury. Then, the heroes break down teams that are bound to disappoint in 2015 before ending the show with the latest edition of "Win Wess' Toaster!"

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
